{"tid":2183924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過喺唔適合場合忍唔到笑","createTime":"2020-09-01T08:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T09:00:18.000Z","uid":2972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f481673f3bc559a593d0866a017cb02b4d55c1c","tid":2183924,"uid":2972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"話說琴日去外父外母屋企食飯<br />\n電視播單新聞係台灣有個風箏節<br />\n有個好大隻ge風箏捲起咗個o靚妹發嚟發去<br />\n我當堂忍唔住&quot;kit&quot;一聲笑咗出嚟<br />\n跟住外父外母同我老婆就開始係咁話我無同情心無人性<br />\n我又唔知做乜應佢哋:&quot;佢發嚟發去喎&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果成晚俾佢哋圍攻<br />\n但我一諗起個畫面就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇破地獄潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f469f802e01bfa21228032cf6d94c3cb7695a44","tid":2183924,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuaP4YP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuaP4YP.gif&h=ce2ee572&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4bb4076850d5bef5ae8a33205bb26dccdb2485f","tid":2183924,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"大奬：足金鳩猴"},{"pid":"a42fda4b1f21c0d4fcbd30336e33fdbf35ae436d","tid":2183924,"uid":90023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"中學分享 俾人推落樓變左殘疾 潮文呢"},{"pid":"3a316f488422fbba551d303b8e975a8e2c698f90","tid":2183924,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"Con會見到啲老鬼懶嚴肅唔覺意笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410002176155ac916f34a88a9f0cd771cdbd4f39","tid":2183924,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"龍哥喪禮<br />\n笑穴"},{"pid":"1ae0d2e43efc3bc9cdfe87b76189605216d97e4e","tid":2183924,"uid":171319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"